rge;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就快十萬人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"60e87226c36664fb30629cf48d43ad4370fceefc","tid":2029772,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"9b0e4559433777a1b731811d13b8b9983a8c6177","tid":2029772,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debfe14b0532772271c387c88235fcaa64a58b01","tid":2029772,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca46f0a96b69a0d454083e302c51030dc679d14","tid":2029772,"uid":140000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4600c054604d851bb987e9372cbec6a2bce137c7","tid":2029772,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883d4c7de0c9350fe3d3414de3